T1  - Does group inclusion hurt financial inclusion? Evidence from ultra-poor members of Ugandan savings groups
AU  - Burlando, Alfredo
AU  - Canidio, Andrea
JO  - Journal of Development Economics
VL  - 128
SP  - 24
EP  - 48
